OL,3,CCan Hamnet turn Shakespeare's tragedy
OL,4,Cinto Oscar gold?
OL,6,FITV News Arts Editor Nina Nannar
OL,7,Fspeaks to Hamnet's stars about how
OL,8,FShakespeare's private grief may have
OL,9,Finspired one of the world's greatest
OL,10,Fplays
OL,12,FOne of my abiding memories of doing
OL,13,Fthis job was three years ago when I
OL,14,Fwas filming in Stratford-upon-Avon.
OL,16,FI was doing an interview with author
OL,17,FMaggie O'Farrell about her best
OL,18,Fselling book Hamnet being adapted for
OL,19,Fthe stage with the Royal Shakespeare
OL,20,FCompany.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
