OL,3,CCan Hamnet turn Shakespeare's tragedy
OL,4,Cinto Oscar gold?
OL,6,FShe looked as if she didn't know how
OL,7,Fmuch she was allowed to reveal of this
OL,8,Ffledgling project.
OL,10,FSo I turned to Chloe. "Are you?" I
OL,11,Fasked.
OL,13,FShe nodded with a smile.
OL,15,FSo I guess I've always felt connected
OL,16,Fto this film - and it's just as well,
OL,17,Fbecause it really is quite wonderful,
OL,18,Fdeeply moving and fantastically acted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
