OL,3,CCan Hamnet turn Shakespeare's tragedy
OL,4,Cinto Oscar gold?
OL,6,FThe author herself co-wrote the
OL,7,Fscreenplay with the director, so those
OL,8,Fwho loved the book will find much to
OL,9,Frecognise.
OL,11,FA study of the family of one of the
OL,12,Fmost famous people to have ever lived,
OL,13,Fit is by necessity a work of fiction,
OL,14,Fbecause although we might feel a
OL,15,Ffamiliarity with Shakespeare the man
OL,16,Fthrough his plays and sonnets, there
OL,17,Fis very little in the way of hard
OL,18,Ffacts about his wife and three
OL,19,Fchildren.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
