OL,3,CCan Hamnet turn Shakespeare's tragedy
OL,4,Cinto Oscar gold?
OL,6,FWe know he married at 18 to a woman
OL,7,Fnamed in her father's will as Agnes
OL,8,FHathaway, but known today as Ann
OL,9,FHathaway. She was older than him and
OL,10,Fpregnant.
OL,12,FThey had three children, one, Hamnet
OL,13,F(a name interchangeable with Hamlet at
OL,14,Fthe time), died aged 11.
OL,16,FShakespeare spent a lot of time in
OL,17,FLondon acting and writing and becoming
OL,18,Fwell, William Shakespeare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
