OL,3,CCan Hamnet turn Shakespeare's tragedy
OL,4,Cinto Oscar gold?
OL,6,FThe film has won widespread acclaim,
OL,7,Fnot least in its two leads. Jessie
OL,8,FBuckley now the favourite to win the
OL,9,FBest Actress Oscar. Paul Mescal has
OL,10,Falso won plaudits for his role.
OL,12,FDirector Chloe Zhao, who is one of
OL,13,Fonly three women to win a Best
OL,14,FDirector Oscar, could well be the only
OL,15,Ffemale nominee this year, which could
OL,16,Fmake headlines.
OL,18,FThere is certainly lot of love for
OL,19,Fthis production.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
