OL,11,FThe film is leading the British charge
OL,12,Fthis year, and whatever the results,
OL,13,Fthis is a film that adds to the
OL,14,FShakespeare story, presenting a side
OL,15,Frarely seen.
OL,17,FWe do not even know for sure what
OL,18,FHamnet died of, though it is widely
OL,19,Fthought that the bubonic plague of
OL,20,Fthat time claimed the boy's life.
