OL,3,CCan Hamnet turn Shakespeare's tragedy
OL,4,Cinto Oscar gold?
OL,6,FIt seems incredible that so little is
OL,7,Fknown about the family.
OL,9,FA recent unearthing of a fragment of a
OL,10,Fletter seemingly addressed to a woman
OL,11,Fthought to be Shakespeare's wife
OL,12,Fsuggests that she did spend time in
OL,13,FLondon with her husband.
OL,15,FBut no one knows for sure.
OL,17,FWhile we wait for irrefutable evidence
OL,18,Fof the Bard's family life, it is left
OL,19,Fto writers and filmmakers to fill the
OL,20,Fgaps - and in this case, to beautiful
OL,21,Feffect.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
